snippet.title: OFFICIAL THE DIVISION 2 - WARLORDS OF NEW YORK - SEASON ONE OVERVIEW
snippet.description:
Despite the SHD agent’s best efforts, a cell of rogue agents has been activated. Intel suggests that this cell is mobilizing and planning an attack in D.C.

Our first Season, "Shadow Tide" will be ongoing for the next 12 weeks starting today, with new activities to participate in and new rewards to earn as you progress. 

Warlords of New York is now available on PC, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One.

http://thedivisiongame.com/buy

Join us now:
